      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOOR BUSTER (2) came back to this level last start when on debut for the Fernie stable and she was just too good, winning by 1.2L. She maps beautifully again today as she continues to work through the grades. Looks beautifully placed and she looks the one to beat. DANCEWITHME (3) just missed in a good form race two back before winning last start as a $1.75 favourite and she looks to be on the way up now. Fiore remains in the irons and the step to 1200m doesn't look an issue. The draw is sticky, but she does have some early speed and she's sure to be in the finish again. FAVAIOS (6) felt the pinch late last start over further and back to 1200m today looks a good move. The inside draw is a big tick for his chances and his best form stacks right up. DIEGO DYNAMITE (7) is third-up today on the back of a strong performance from the front. Keep safe. THE LIONS' GATE (5) is not to be discounted on recent efforts.",
